query:
SELECT dataset_id   AS "id: _",
                   owner_id     AS "owner_id: _",
                   owner_name,
                   dataset_name AS name,
                   created_at   AS "created_at: _",
                   kind         AS "kind: _"
            FROM dataset_entries
            WHERE (owner_id, dataset_name) IN (SELECT *
                                               FROM UNNEST($1::TEXT[],
                                                           $2::TEXT[]))
            ORDER BY owner_name, dataset_name
